import React from 'react'
import "./MarketingHub.css"
import { Box, Button, HStack,Image } from '@chakra-ui/react'
const MarketingHub = () => {
  return (
    <>
        <Box>
            <Box>
                <HStack>
                    <Image src='https://static.hsappstatic.net/ui-addon-upgrades/static-9.6877/js/img/MarketingHub_Icon.svg' alt='Marketing hub logo' />
                </HStack>
            </Box>
        </Box>
    </>
  )
}

export default MarketingHub
